.0, \"rank\": 1.6530355730575615e-15, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The jacket was green cotton with a navy and gold detail, lined with fabric listing previous gold medallists.\", \"from\": 6253, \"to\": 6361, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2012 was also the first year the Olympic team announced the uniforms before the ceremony took place.\", \"from\": 6363, \"to\": 6463, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are announcing the uniforms to you before the opening ceremony for the first time,\\\" Olympic rower, Nick Green said at the time.\", \"from\": 6465, \"to\": 6596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6568, \"end\": 6578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Green_(rower)\", \"score\": 0.6528385340174219, \"rank\": 0.5161290322581477, \"text\": \"Nick Green\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Green_(rower)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Green_(rower)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is historic.\", \"from\": 6598, \"to\": 6614, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We know London will be historic.\", \"from\": 6615, \"to\": 6647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6623, \"end\": 6629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6530355730575615e-15, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today, I believe, is a great historic event.\", \"from\": 6648, \"to\": 6692, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The look was completed with a pair of white Dunlop Volleys.\", \"from\": 6694, \"to\": 6753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6738, \"end\": 6744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dunlop_Rubber\", \"score\": 0.9993113265446287, \"rank\": 0.00067247839695111